{"tid":1794191,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人記性好差","createTime":"2019-12-23T02:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T23:45:38.000Z","uid":240973,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf6fd28b5668b3aaacae76c07b3faa9df110320","tid":1794191,"uid":240973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:45:19.000Z","msg":"以前細個成日日夜顛倒，直到有時連自己尋晚食咩早幾日做都啲咩都完全唔記得<br />\n係認真諗都諗唔到<br />\n個陣開始驚，寫左兩年日記作息好少少(都3,4點訓) 又好似好返啲<br />\n<br />\n而家既話 記性都係偏差<br />\n三年前大約咩時間搬屋都唔記得<br />\n有時自己幾多歲都唔記得，比人問起都要諗要即刻計<br />\n另外時間觀念好差唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e356945c58124abd87b2165f4bcf688690610434","tid":1794191,"uid":114487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgwZ4tD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgwZ4tD.jpg&h=52b479a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGepv8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGepv8D.jpg&h=265d7544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocgLfAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocgLfAm.jpg&h=e2a8e121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"389dbd249d16288b77aa1fd7eae8a8cb5ce2a48e","tid":1794191,"uid":71166,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:47:51.000Z","msg":"我 <br />\n特別對數字唔敏感<br />\n例如你話1751<br />\n我會兩秒就話1157或唔記得咗成組數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e20a054207e55cacfabdbc34e042efeacee8f0a","tid":1794191,"uid":122134,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:51:51.000Z","msg":"其實好正常<br />\n好多人.....<br />\n<br />\n算啦 我唔記得自己想講咩"},{"pid":"8e86d993632fc8580a384f4018a0d40497cfec48","tid":1794191,"uid":240973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e20a054207e55cacfabdbc34e042efeacee8f0a","tid":1794191,"uid":122134,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":